      const prompt = `You are a local travel insider with deep knowledge of ${destination}. Discover 3-5 authentic hidden gems that most tourists never find.

🗺️ TRAVELER PROFILE:
• Destination: ${destination}
• Primary Interests: ${preferences.interests.join(", ")}
• Daily Budget: ₹${preferences.budget} per person
• Trip Duration: ${preferences.duration} days
• Travel Style: ${preferences.travelStyle}

🔍 HIDDEN GEMS CRITERIA:
1. NOT mentioned in typical guidebooks
2. Frequented by locals, not tourists  
3. Authentic cultural experiences
4. Within budget constraints (₹50 - ₹${Math.floor(preferences.budget * 0.8)} per person)
5. Match interests: ${preferences.interests.join(", ")}
6. Safe and accessible locations

💎 EXAMPLES OF HIDDEN GEMS:
• Local family-run eateries serving regional specialties
• Neighborhood markets where locals shop
• Traditional workshops where artisans work
• Lesser-known viewpoints or natural spots
• Cultural spaces hosting local events
• Historic sites without crowds

🎯 OUTPUT FORMAT:
Return ONLY a valid JSON array. No explanatory text.

[
  {
    "id": "gem-unique-id",
    "title": "Descriptive Name of Hidden Gem",
    "description": "Detailed explanation of what makes this place special and unique",
